ir\nreported values results in an unresolvable tension between the two observations\nat more than $3\\sigma$ level which can be a hint towards a serious systematic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2013 16:39:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2014 08:01:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-14"}
