c path integral is the principal task of the present paper,\nand it is done in two independent ways. Gauge-fixing and the background\nindependence of the resulting path integral are discussed in the appendices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2013 19:12:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
